title: S2, Ep3: Hella Open
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
Let’s be honest, life just isn’t always so simple. Crissle and Fran talk all the complicated factors of love, work and friendship that Issa, Molly and Lawrence face.

Join in the conversation on social media using the hashtag #insecuriTEA. And don’t forget to follow @LSNPodcasts.
